<http://example.org/A> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://example.org/B> .
<http://example.org/Alice> <http://ont.example.org/livesIn> "London" .
<http://example.org/Alice> <http://ont.example.org/worksFor> <http://example.org/CompanyA> .
<http://example.org/Bob> <http://ont.example.org/livesIn> "New York" .
<http://example.org/Bob> <http://ont.example.org/worksFor> <http://example.org/CompanyB> .
<http://example.org/C> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://example.org/B> .
<http://example.org/Charlie> <http://ont.example.org/livesIn> "London" .
<http://example.org/Charlie> <http://ont.example.org/worksFor> <http://example.org/CompanyA> .
<http://example.org/CompanyA> <http://ont.example.org/locatedIn> "United Kingdom" .
<http://example.org/CompanyB> <http://ont.example.org/locatedIn> "USA" .
<http://example.org/D> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://example.org/E> .
<http://example.org/Dave> <http://ont.example.org/livesIn> "Berlin" .
<http://example.org/Eve> <http://ont.example.org/livesIn> "Paris" .
<http://example.org/bob2> <http://ont.example.org/hasName> "Fred" .
<http://example.org/carol> <http://ont.example.org/worksFor> "Sally" .
<http://example.org/carol> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Person> .
<http://example.org/carol> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/knows> <http://example.org/nmg> .
<http://example.org/dave> <http://ont.example.org/hasName> "Alice" .
<http://example.org/dave> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Person> .
<http://example.org/jane> <http://ont.example.org/age> 30 .
<http://example.org/jane> <http://ont.example.org/hasName> "Jane" .
<http://example.org/mywork> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.0/creator> <http://example.org/john> .
<http://example.org/yourwork> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/creator> <http://example.org/jane> .
